<h1>Maria Brophy</h1>

<h2><a href="/">/now</a>: <a href="http://mariabrophy.com/now">mariabrophy.com/now</a></h2>

<h2>Location:</h2>
<p>
San Clemente
CA
United States
</p>

<h2>Professional title:</h2>
<p>
Consultant to creative entrepreneurs.
</p>

<h2>What do you do?</h2>
<p>
Helping artists master the business of art, one strategy at a time
</p>

<h2>Why?</h2>
<p>
It comes so easily to me; I've got a fire inside to figure out the right business path for each artist I work with; like putting pieces to a puzzle together.   When an artist says "thank God I found you, I'm finally getting results" I know I'm doing what I'm meant to do.
</p>

<h2>Recent thought or epiphany?</h2>
<p>
That you can change your outside world with your inner thoughts.   With that realization, I feel incredibly powerful.
</p>

<h2>What should we read?</h2>
<p>
Dr. Joe Dispenza's “YOU ARE THE PLACEBO”
</p>

